{{Flavour|A potion of beneficial mutation}}

The '''potion of gain strength''' bestows one level of the [[good mutations#Improved Attributes|Improved Attributes]] mutation, which gives your character +1 [[Strength]] (cumulative up to +14 points). Hard to find, and useful for melee-oriented characters, or those who are dangerously low on strength.

The mutation can be removed by the normal means (eg, a [[potion of cure mutation]], Zin's [[Zin#Given Abilities|Cure All Mutations]] ability). Unlike other sources of mutations, the potion isn't hindered by an [[amulet of resist mutation]] (but ''is'' by the [[Good mutations#Mutation Resistance|Mutation Resistance]] mutation). Use of this potion does not offend [[Zin]].

{{crawlquote|''You feel stronger.''}}

==History==
In [[0.13]] this potion was replaced with the [[potion of beneficial mutation]].
